title: [Mist Harbor Proper, Sewers]
description: Tiny rivulets slip down the northern and southern passages and meet in the center of the tunnel's floor where they create a tiny pool.  Rounded, white pebbles form a small barrier around the pool that prevents it from spilling into the main walking area of the passage.  A ragged torch provides illumination for the immediate area, though it does little to illuminate the incline to the north.
